Coordinating Committee of Karpaz have put on time restrictions on essential businesses. Pharmacies, supermarkets, butchers, suppliers of livestock food and agricultural pesticides will be open between 8:00-12:00 where they will only accept orders on phone calls, and the delivery of the orders will take place between 12:00-15:00. When butchers' have sold their reserves, they will close. Bakehouses will be open for production between 20:00-08:00 and deliveries to supermarkets, grocery stores, etc. will take place between 08:00-10:00. People who have livestock can take of them between 08:00-18:00 if they live in a different district than their stockyard, and between 08.00-10:00 or 15:00-17:00 if they live in the same district. People who have greenhouses can operate between 08:00-12:00. Beekeepers can operate between 15:00-17:00. In all steps, hygiene will be the first concern.
